message:
A new environment has been set up for Red Hat Process Automation Manager 7.
The username/password for accessing Business Central Monitoring is

    Username: ${KIE_ADMIN_USER}
    Password: ${KIE_ADMIN_PWD}

Both sets of KIE servers are configured with the username/password

    Username: ${KIE_SERVER_USER}
    Password: ${KIE_SERVER_PWD}

Please be sure to create the secrets named "${BUSINESS_CENTRAL_HTTPS_SECRET}" and "${KIE_SERVER_HTTPS_SECRET}" containing the
${BUSINESS_CENTRAL_HTTPS_KEYSTORE} and ${KIE_SERVER_HTTPS_KEYSTORE} files used for serving secure content.
